8:
Sometimes you lift poor people up so that they are no longer sitting in the dust,\q2 and you raise up needy people so that they are no longer sitting on heaps of ashes;
\q1 you cause them to sit next to princes;
\q2 you cause them to sit on seats where people who are highly honored sit.
\q1 Yahweh, you are the one who laid the foundations of the earth,
\q2 and you have set the whole world on those foundations.


\q1
